{"tid":1777329,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何 君 堯 稱 L 型 傷 疤 是 「愛的記號」","createTime":"2019-12-10T06:43:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T11:57:46.000Z","uid":215823,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"634a0c590165ad8328b638edcf5470ee687112f6","tid":1777329,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T06:43:47.000Z","msg":"近日，何君堯二度接受央視節目《面對面》訪問，並稱對獲頒政法大學名譽博士學位感自豪，「是國家給我一個認同」。此外，他談及上月屯門街站遇襲，形容 L 型傷疤是「愛的記號」，又將自己比作盧溝橋事變中與日軍決一死戰的防衛官。<br />\n<br />\n節目主持人問及何君堯 11 月 6 日在屯門擺街站期間遇襲一事，何君堯指事件給他帶來恐懼，現時不敢看有關影片，「因為看這個視頻的時候給我一個很震撼的感覺」。主持人又提到遇襲全程有人拍攝，事後亦被質疑是一場秀，何君堯則表示拍照作用是「防範性」。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯又指，現時傷勢已痊愈，<strong>因傷疤是L型，他笑稱那是「Love」&mdash;「愛的記號」。</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z2FaXoC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz2FaXoC.jpg&h=cacc934d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他又將自己比作盧溝橋事變時與日軍決一死戰的防衞官，「其實這個兵很孤單，站在最前端，但是他不是逃兵。他要做的就是，你不可以進來，你甚麼理由也不可以。」他表示，<strong>「君堯只是做一個不要逃跑的士兵，談不上甚麼偉大，我就是做我分內的事情」</strong>，稱自己對作為一個「中國人」感自豪。"},{"pid":"2657325af877b73c6f7d7786678ed67f34c24a58","tid":1777329,"uid":64985,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T06:47:45.000Z","msg":"L stands for LunYeung"},{"pid":"9f6761b53d209435ad67aee5deedbdf3f60cb43e","tid":1777329,"uid":269515,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T06:52:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mikimTA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmikimTA.png&h=06abae70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eetcrkh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEetcrkh.png&h=3f1bf777&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c6GQXrZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc6GQXrZ.png&h=32b8babc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VWEnOyE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVWEnOyE.png&